Can I not wait 30 minutes, or even a few hours, or a day?  Of course I can. 
It’s not a matter of life or death, or national security, or anything important really.
- Leo Babauta
%
Not knowing isn’t bad. It’s just different. 
And really, I think there’s something minimalist about it. 
Let’s let go of the need to know, every second of the day.
Let our minds wander around in the dark for abit.
- Leo Babauta
